transfer.description: Transfers `rawAmount` of tokens from the caller's account to `dst`.

transferFrom.description: Transfers `rawAmount` of tokens from `src` to `dst` on behalf of `src`.

constructor.description: Initializes the contract with the given account address.

approve.description: Sets the allowance of `spender` to `rawAmount` tokens.

allowance.description: Returns the remaining number of tokens that `spender` is allowed to spend on behalf of `account`.

decimals.description: Returns the number of decimal places used by the token.

name.description: Returns the name of the token.

symbol.description: Returns the symbol of the token.

totalSupply.description: Returns the total supply of tokens.

getCurrentVotes.description: Returns the current number of votes held by `account`.

getPriorVotes.description: Returns the number of votes held by `account` at a specific block number.

delegateBySig.description: Delegates voting power to `delegatee` using a signature.

checkpoints.description: Returns the checkpoint information of `account` at a specific index.

numCheckpoints.description: Returns the number of checkpoints for `account`.

DELEGATION_TYPEHASH.description: Returns the type hash for delegation.
